-- Merafe Resources Expecting Recovery in Ferrochrome Market Through to 2013
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2010-11-09T06:58:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/merafe-resources-sees-ferrochrome-market-recovery-through-2013.html
Merafe Resources Ltd. said it expects
a recovery in the ferrochrome market through to 2013 because of
global economic growth coupled with no new capacity coming on
stream in South Africa “in the near future.”  Merafe commented in a presentation published on its website
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  